						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 25 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mahādēva at Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai by Mallaṉ Araṅgaṉ (a resident) of the <hi rend="bold">Mañjanattār-Vēḷam at Tañjāvūr.</hi> This was to be maintained by the temple servants <hi rend="italic">(patipādamūlattār)</hi> and the <hi rend="italic">dēvakarmi.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
